<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Givingly: skill-based volunteering in Toronto</title>
  <meta name='description' content="Marketplace for skill-based volunteer projects in Toronto. We welcome not-for-profit and charities to post volunteer projects that enhance their organizational capabilities." >

  <meta name='keywords' content="volunteer, volunteer toronto, volunteer opportunities, volunteer consulting, consulting for a cause, consulting for not-for-profit, not-for-profit, pro bono, pro bono toronto, pro bono opportunities, nonprofit, volunteer for non profit, fundraising, volunteer consulting services, not-for-profit marketing" >

